257
00:14:27,763 --> 00:14:29,264
- Kenny!
- [all shouting at once]

258
00:14:29,265 --> 00:14:30,765
- Kenny, Kenny!
- I'll fucking kill you!

259
00:14:30,766 --> 00:14:32,434
- Where is she?
- I can't! I can't!

260
00:14:32,435 --> 00:14:34,811
