460
00:25:07,027 --> 00:25:10,279
- Look at me. Hey, hey.
- [panting]

461
00:25:10,280 --> 00:25:12,281
- You're gonna be okay.
- [panting]

462
00:25:12,282 --> 00:25:15,451
