467
00:25:31,843 --> 00:25:34,429
- Dad, just...
- Nobody comes upstairs.

468
00:25:36,098 --> 00:25:39,309
- You make sure of that, okay?
- Yeah.

469
00:25:41,311 --> 00:25:44,272
What happens next...

470
00:25:44,273 --> 00:25:47,191
