to talk to you.

495
00:27:37,219 --> 00:27:40,180
[dramatic music playing]

496
00:27:58,115 --> 00:27:59,490
Here.

497
00:27:59,491 --> 00:28:00,534
Okay.

498
00:28:05,622 --> 00:28:07,456
