512
00:29:16,109 --> 00:29:17,444
Is that...

513
00:29:19,404 --> 00:29:21,280
Is that Eloise?

514
00:29:21,281 --> 00:29:23,950
I think so.

515
00:29:27,370 --> 00:29:28,955
All I found were pieces.

516
00:29:32,083 --> 00:29:33,043
[whimpering]

517
00:29:33,044 --> 00:29:35,170
She was so small.

518
00:29:37,297 --> 00:29:39,298
